summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a franchise from King County to construct, maintain and operate a feeder water main along Southwest 107th Street, Southwest 106th Place and Southwest 106th Street between 16th Avenue Southwest and 30th Avenue Southwest, as therein more particularly set forth, for the Southwest 107th Street, et al, Feeder Water Main project and authorizing and directing the Superintendent of Water to sign said franchise for and on behalf of the City of Seattle.
